 <PERSON> Bryan </PERSON> <PERSON> Brumley </PERSON> covers international affairs for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> from <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
