h have included questions about <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON>' patriotism and jokes about his height. `` If it continues, you have to respond,'' he said. `` I think that's unfortunate, but I think it's very clear what kind of campaign the Republicans are running and I think we're going to have to deal with it.''
