he most beautiful thing we have.'' <PERSON> Zanone </PERSON> sobbed quietly. Some politicians in <LOCATION> Italy </LOCATION> have demanded the squadron be disbanded, but <PERSON> Zanone </PERSON> and <PERSON> Pisano </PERSON> said earlier this week the team would continue to fly.
