ti </PERSON> said <LOCATION> Iraq </LOCATION> was `` raising a lot of preconditions,'' including clearing the waterway, which is choked with silt and sunken ships. But he said there was no deadlock. Both <PERSON> Velayati </PERSON> and <PERSON> Aziz </PERSON> said they would remain in <LOCATION> Geneva </LOCATION> as long as necessary.
