ndex of all its listed common stocks gained .15 to 148.81. At the <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Stock </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION>, the market value index was up .11 at 295.02. Volume on the <ORGANIZATION> Big </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Board </ORGANIZATION> came to 61.72 million shares at noontime, against 49.69 million at the same point Tuesday.
