sday adds the purchase by Carnival of all I.M. Skaugen A-S, <ORGANIZATION> Johnson </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Line </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> AB </ORGANIZATION> and <ORGANIZATION> EFFOA-Finland </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Steamship </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>. <ORGANIZATION> Ltd. </ORGANIZATION> holdings in <LOCATION> Royal </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Caribbean </LOCATION> and Admiral Carnival operates seven ships sailing on three -, four - and seven-day cruises to the <LOCATION> Bahamas </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Caribbean </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Mexican </LOCATION> The company also operates a casino in the <LOCATION> Bahamas </LOCATION> and is building a luxury hotel at an adjacent site. Royal <LOCATION> Caribbean </LOCATION> operates primarily in the <LOCATION> Caribbean </LOCATION>, while Admiral sails in both the <LOCATION> Caribbean </LOCATION> and the <LOCATION> Pacific </LOCATION>.
